  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375 fahrenheit.",
    "in a clay tajine, mix together yogurt, ginger, garlic, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, black pepper, cumin, coriander, and knead in a mixing bowl.",
    "add in the iceberg lettuce and toss until coated with the yogurt mixture.",
    "transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "garnish with fresh cilantro before serving.",
    "serve warm or at room temperature."
